title.en: "Omae ga Kawari ni Shine" to Iwareta Watashi. Imouto no Migawari ni Reikoku na Henkyou Haku no Moto e Totsugi, Shiawase wo Teniireru
Akumeitakai Ryoushu ni Totsugu Koto ni Narimashita ga Mainichi Shiawase desu
Henkyou no Binbou Hakushaku ni Totsugu Koto ni natta no de Ryouchi Kaikaku ni Hagemimasu
Senjou no Seijo - Imouto no Kawari ni Koushaku Kishi ni Totsugu Koto ni narimashita ga, Ima wa Shiawase desu
Nibante no Onna - Utahime to shite no Hokori wo Mune ni, Saigo no Gohoukou wo Itashimasu
Ikenie to shite Surerareta no de, Henkyou Hakke ni Jibun wo Urimasu
Shiitagerareta Hanayome wa Reitetsu Ryou-sama ni Dekiaisareru
Imouto no Migawari de Totsuida Hazu ga, Douyara Watashi ga Shin no Seijo Datta you desu
Zessei no Akujo wa Maouji-sama ni Chouaisareru
Akuma de Kore wa Koi janai!
Hakushaku-ke wo Mamoru Tame ni Toriaezu Konyakushimashita - Neet no Reijou wa Shuubun wo Harashi Ijiwaru na Koushaku-ke ni Taikou suru Tame Ichikabachika no Konyaku wo Ketsuden suru
Kokurou Ou to Shirogane no Niehime
Ryuushi no Hanayome - Shinryoku no Otome wa Seiryuu no Shugosha ni Aisareru
Kanpeki Sugite Kawaige ga nai to Konyaku Hakisareta Seijo wa Ringoku ni Urareru
Azamukare Seijo to Shugoryuu no Konyaku

title.ja: Yakutatazu to Iwareta node, Watashi no Ie wa Dokuritsu Shimasu!
